title: Bug 49235: ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<? classSet is not expected class
description: Bug 49235: The ServletContainerInitializer onStartup(Set<Class<?> classSet is not returning the expected output. The current output is 'MySomeClass'.
OB: The current output is 'MySomeClass', but I expect the output to be 'MySomeClass'. This issue is not yet implemented in the Servlet 3.0 specification. The code works fine on Glassfish 3.0.
